WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:05.000
lucas! come on. it's me. open up.

00:11.000 --> 00:12.350
look. i am sorry i am late,

00:12.385 --> 00:13.700
but i couldn't get away.

00:13.735 --> 00:15.000
are you there?

00:16.600 --> 00:17.900
hey. hey.

00:18.700 --> 00:20.850
are you looking for lucas?

00:20.885 --> 00:22.542
uh,no. i'll just come back.

00:22.577 --> 00:24.165
well,he should be here.

00:24.200 --> 00:26.465
his car's parked in his space and mine.

00:26.500 --> 00:28.500
could you tell him that
those parallel white lines

00:28.535 --> 00:29.765
actually serve a purpose?

00:29.800 --> 00:31.500
i had to park on the street again.

